fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.blueprints.io

Class BlueprintsNaiveHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.io.persistence.AbstractPersistenceHandler<BlueprintsPersistenceBackend>
      • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.blueprints.io.AbstractBlueprintsHandler
        • fr.inria.atlanmod.neoemf.data.blueprints.io.BlueprintsNaiveHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    InputHandler, PersistenceHandler

    public class BlueprintsNaiveHandler
extends AbstractBlueprintsHandler
    A PersistenceHandler for BlueprintsPersistenceBackends, without key conflict resolution.

    Unlike the BlueprintsAwareHandler, this handler does not solve key conflicts. However, they are detected and an exception is raised to avoid the creation of an unusable back-end.
